{
  "stem": "4963.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, one incident which I will never forget was that they were-- the laws were circulated that no people who go out in the workforce are permitted to bring anything back.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, they-- they said there will be punishment by death.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they caught one person, and they made a-- made him as a-- how should I say it, as a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] picture, you know, for everybody to see.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they-- they took him, and they took him out into a field and drove everybody out to-- into that big field and-- to actually witness the hanging.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember watching it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember putting the rope around-- the rope being placed on his-- on his neck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and as they elevated, as they-- as he was the elevated and finally the expression on his-- and they made us look at it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But as I said, I was-- being a child, I guess I approached everything with-- with kind of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] child's point of view of-- of not breaking down, of looking at it in-- in a curiosity way.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was left there for three days, hanging and with big signs and big--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember that there were big horns that they would go around with, big loud speakers looks like horn and broadcasting over the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see what happens to him?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what will happen to you if you disobey the law.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What had he brought in?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He brought in bread and sausage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were hidden under his clothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's one way of-- of bringing the cloth-- of bringing the food in.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
